title: Romy & Michele's High School Reunion - More Music From The M
description:
Source: 1997 CD

Some good tracks "She Blinded Me with Science" being one of the best! Speaking of which, listen to that song and at 1:45 there is what seems to be a skip followed by some reverb. I think that is a slight remix b/c I don't recall that being in the original version....maybe it was...

Lisa Kudrow received a degree in Biology from Vassar College, and Mira Sorvino a degree in Asian Studies from Harvard University, so during production of Romy and Michele, they nicknamed each other "Smart" and "Smarter".
